<p>One idle afternoon in the summer, Ben (8) was playing with some Silly
Putty, and asked, "How come no one does claymation with Silly Putty?"
</p>

<p>No one had an answer, so with Max (14) as cinematographer with a still
camera, Ben started animating.  Fifteen minutes later, we had this basic
proof of concept:</p>

