<p>It can be done! Silliputtimation is possible!</p>

<p>BTW: this is the first video I've uploaded to YouTube.  They do a good
job of the process, making it very straightforward to get content on their
site.  I liked their wording for three-option radio buttons, for example,
for allowing comments on videos.  The choices are "Yes", "No", and "Kinda",
meaning moderated.
</p>

